12:47.956 --> 12:53.083
I'm grateful for an answered prayer and I'm sure you're a grateful answered prayer.

12:53.143 --> 13:01.975
Some of the stuff is some kind of halfway pressurizing one of our sister churches.

13:02.075 --> 13:04.018
