13:04.098 --> 13:28.434
United Church they have a magazine they put out called What if it's not tomorrow's world cuz that's Beyond today thinking beyond today, and they had a really good article in there there November December or This last year and so some of the stuff come out of that some plagiarizing a little bit and along that line even

13:28.546 --> 13:38.599
The living church has a good publication too, so if you have some friends or relatives or something rather, you want them to bite off a little bit.

13:38.679 --> 13:46.548
I don't care which church they go to, as long as they get the message of God and they change their mind or change their attitude and they're living a kind of life.

13:47.149 --> 13:50.994
And if it's for them to come to our church, that's fine, you know, we're good.

13:51.042 --> 13:56.671
But I don't mind helping them out a little bit, you know, because they got some really, really good stuff.

13:56.751 --> 14:04.203
And the TV real cast on Sunday for the living church is really, really good, very strong.

14:05.466 --> 14:10.854
They mentioned quite a bit the Sabbath and then the Holy Days go into detail.

14:10.934 --> 14:14.681
So they've got some really good ones on local station on Sunday mornings.

14:15.802 --> 14:18.066
And I didn't mean to digress that much.

14:22.882 --> 14:29.094
And we're grateful for answered prayer and even an answered prayer.

14:29.154 --> 14:31.698
And I've made a mention this several years ago, too.

14:31.718 --> 14:33.542
There was no country song.

14:34.704 --> 14:36.567
Thank God for unanswered prayer.

14:36.587 --> 14:40.114
The essence of that, I see somebody shaking your head.

14:40.258 --> 14:46.206
Some of you, the guy when he was young, he prayed, oh, God, let this girl be mine.

14:46.247 --> 14:47.969
You know, I just, I'd give anything.

14:47.989 --> 14:51.774
God just let the, and I think some of you out here probably have done the same thing.

14:51.835 --> 14:57.723
