15:02.149 --> 15:08.338
And when I started dating my wife, or she started dating me or whatever, once she tricked me on to date her,

15:08.674 --> 15:13.499
No, it's one of the best blessings I've ever had outside of God's Holy Spirit.

15:14.180 --> 15:17.263
But when I started dating her, I really liked her a lot.

15:17.944 --> 15:19.446
But I didn't tell God that.

15:19.506 --> 15:25.172
I didn't want to jinx it because all these others, you know, and I've always been kind of romantic.

15:25.913 --> 15:29.016
But all the others I pray about, you know, God, let this be the one.

15:29.196 --> 15:31.239
Well, you know, I'll just spend my life with her.

15:31.819 --> 15:37.906
And I didn't do that with my wife until we'd already, well, we got married, I guess.

15:38.498 --> 15:44.905
But I didn't want to jinx it, because anyway, but I think God for a lot of them answered prayers that I had.

15:45.766 --> 15:52.333
Anyway, she's taken, so if I die, don't, anyway.

15:53.655 --> 16:00.443
But yeah, like I said, that's what Charlie Kirk, I think would agree with that.

16:00.483 --> 16:07.090
You know, one of his big gills was, you know, get married, raise kids, have a family,

16:07.234 --> 16:11.239
I don't know anything much better for me in my life.

16:11.299 --> 16:17.766
Now, there's some people that marriage is just not for them and maybe they don't have a big drive in the other direction.

16:17.826 --> 16:18.527
That's okay.

16:19.448 --> 16:27.557
But to me, that's one of the best advantages that a young man can have is a good woman and a woman can have a good man.

16:27.617 --> 16:32.663
Anyway, and I know a lot of you are thankful too.

16:32.803 --> 16:35.346
